*9th-level death knight feature*
<div style='margin-top:-4px;'></div>

### Aura of Dread
*10th-level death knight feature*
<div style='margin-top:-4px;'></div>

As long as you are conscious, whenever a creature within 10 feet of you targets you with an attack, they must first make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, they have disadvantage on the attack roll. A creature immune to the frightened condition is immune to this effect.

At 18th level, the range of this aura increases to 30 feet.

[Source.](https://www.dandwiki.com/wiki/Death_Knight_(5e_Subclass)#:~:text=Aura%20of%20the%20Damned.,attack%20rolls%20made%20against%20you.)

