### Knight of the Unholy
**Instead of a permanent ghoul, should the subclass have the ability to temporarily raise a dead enemy, like the hexblade?**

**Make this rune focus on the concept of unholiness, over disease or undead servants. Like inverted paladin and priest abilities, mockeries of the Light. Seems like the sort of thing Arthas would enjoy.**

***There still can be undead bolstering abilities and diseases, but as inverses of paladin abilities. Like Turn Undead becomes Bolster Undead, Lay on Hands becomes spreading disease, etc.***

